 font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国大使可能只是在反击他们所认为的基于规则的国际秩序的虚伪。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;不管怎样，他们最近几周发生了数量惊人的外交事件，激怒了整个欧洲和中东的政体。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在法国，驻巴黎大使馆转发了美国国务院警告“暴力激进左派”正在抬头的消息后，查尔斯·库什纳大使&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/5vgimMKlUaZkiDEuwRNm-OEbPYZ6FbIpyWZyLowbORqyHJTQq5BqnsGV-s5pwKVKshmNG1cPpw92gPrTF5zyGByOCdZZR-EK7VQ1SAIDluwlEK6pJVmZUHOXFFwyDknOv-xWRzffJugIMbOdsBFNAFSOMYhUKmS05jMytDGgMkknWGP4j41Jsxomhwb4LpzF6nSoYKDFHfgE3msb2Zni9EGcv_Ir95wPQs-So6S8OY5n7A5PVEqkScY6bDoIjaOmWHpng6RYJgwtODaLE62wx9zcrJCGEoqxcID_pbA6hx6garDDOzLLiyplxQnuL2T7CV-DOBhSsY1cDMro5h2kdcTTVr7aE3N-CCUcYqdjsbiwFaT3y7IfpqY4pVLxOjc1oyNKyqjonx_IXTJcIjnwf07d6PmnzGY_E8xyUN-mGFaNLA2fTlb0nZkym7To8yTx-OaykDhFl0dazfobXRdDmFj-2utGCcnIAbJ_rR8gyG7jRNtpeBOwyY7AqmmkGQix42R40wsnFcmOwbkaZOhaHw/fiBPZ2FcT0d5D2ntaaznl-nkKRDaJoSY/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="库什纳缺席后法国取消其大使访问权"&gt;陷入了困境&lt;/a&gt;。它引用了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/L3EM1p9tftHzH7jbRSrZNTsnOL6S_YFgiKNGVI9c1I22SDdYiHJT6_3k8x4p2cbbzd41vDzrAxOaSfHB8K8hUtKsMvp189gBvqPQ9EQ1YhzUgOK_z-DWAFvZgauKdijA0KnRE8EmhexPVejY-3aKRAIcX5BghPSIczeqmEtJ3BSzgp1eR-UfOnSHb0xCyNVB0EfChEIi379wi29J3vaj876mx9JhkZ2j-2VQBLcfESnUP1_WPWB2E6WJQzQV9dF6WzgV_LBCQ9UA_YmBg4bCOQxo_8uwDPmYtoutRFQgoVrV08AAeB1Gz-d_tcMDVrYiE45WWOaq1WSDagyv83bYC-CYv8uzD_Oj_N8YXajupptwgtTigB1Lup2JNMV_NFE25JCge3-0idBapHEXqRjNhMnjslF2eTo-4OC8yVxPGgZOj4LEs0z0PzUfEM3Njg35gdpxMz_I9w6Vyi6O_DBSHi0bD54o69MJv86VhaEtLqRQf1UTnqTiEo7uuXgOQyBMFyrIy0vfBkYAn8gI56MHNkA/xE9sTeOxvgAfQJ325bParcx0tmkIqx4p/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="活动人士在政治活动中死于打斗后，法国陷入边缘"&gt;一名被法国媒体描述为极右翼活动人士的 23 岁男子被杀事件&lt;/a&gt;作为公共安全受到威胁的证据。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;库什纳昨天在外交部传唤时没有出席， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/OppH-5gzp4t2LTR3uqDagPKYXZK4hJKVXA0d3bJvM8sK6aZ1RnWSW_5