;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普上周在最高法院罕见落败，周一&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Zh4KEq6_HctD1SxtlNik1xDh8KvKYrlUHK6B0aBKxIAWMcE5UvhYOAZUhz554jbwJqaHNptC412fm-_yVEP8RpCcj-VHm4XZ7V4UN--QS68__3-_w2_Dxt5ssAzA8wGJU-C9x46dN6iSryuRcGP0upKnrFNk6PoPeydXcFb0SBqguFPG5fPT6ppsNw0zl92JlXq5b1Dr-3dxVwAQ02x5QP38hVHQgXjANjn7H62QDSBud-OhOte5Sv46lKZPx4asUat7QsFInabxNdeVWV8fs-9U21e1or46JvRRcdW5MerIyURBivvnvNHT5-OBFS1lcOuzeALjWNKfaN9TDEklNovl_Ws1TR7JgwSzeWylmRA2RABY08uNlAyEEg/4gJ9_EsrSNGXpmjuF_bL4VdEDxg7hC22/18" target="_blank"&gt;继续引起共鸣，&lt;/a&gt;因为美国贸易伙伴重新评估过去一年与总统达成的妥协和协议。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;欧盟冻结了对美国协议的批准，直到特朗普在近一年前发起的全球贸易战中白宫新战略尘埃落定。欧盟对特朗普最新关税提案的初步解读是， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HCkEW3rkkqdB7j3aJQlaoxk4uV-Rd3mJ98NugQJFv0-RjKdfSH5XTQp0fsrPojkLxfYNWr9i9Ti9rreq10hfbJpAjzmvRBGdEnbuB7aQPY3sxnvra2Vb3aCtktt_s8KbJRi84qUJOuN7CpQUkQUjr5oxGyZxlp-LX3faqm58W37gxOn8GCqDnoeuusNvAO_F_cVrmoPHhzH2p_MsUzYGIlIEyGfOj2WVMAsEGYc1E-2aema5Cjnw7ufA73Bmjrf6gN2UpVT-afQ2W-88xRhB0cN8XEaE1PvizHMwmqAriBsZJsIdnd-sbJnUOT6MEv6KI1QMgu6yYOjQiZhUPl_Wt0o6iP66PqeKcjzOpcEsRFPILBphWEUw4Yj6TA/YMNIsX4_XXfGcaOe43nK2QEc3K8PAVD2/18" target="_blank"&gt;这些提案违反了去年与他达成的协议&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; “我们希望弄清楚情况，”欧洲议会贸易委员会主席贝恩德·兰格周一表示。 “我们希望美国明确表示他们尊重该协议，因为这是一个关键因素。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HgO-8CEmskSfPO_Y9X7L0fui0tO_7dTgzpPtnXvgdJXIPAq7-ZZ02qD31Z_bM0xRHgIJqNG7z3wqgdmqnq8qBQ3cNjIk5NdSjEwTEssR-wm1mM33XtleiYwRrOy9bQi6KBoQ1veIeCtyiL4J74apBoQ3Xnh-RsCISOG46UzNmzAJZN9A9Kc3VtFPG1hCFMBWWVuC1Es2vRavN1bPp9NLow58ki0FJb1VHV5hRRFJv3iTITiHPcEUhy3cIyOsPLkwMgZYoyhLrUcRbZOTfT_3v9TZ44DaaqSLrEk_s_7X2_CNNFUngt7plCJE2qxc2dHj_QkxkHDdD4a_P-dJyKnAMk8BDYTGCPreVO8ynsF8RPdsSexgKFbprrnSbA/u84Zc1kB9obM879fCwCr66ONnk3WGl1l/18" target="_blank"&gt;则以新的威胁&lt;/a&gt;作为回应。但随着中期选举的临近以及他的支持率&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cT7Mmf2UT71ERynjDddMV74egxgIOQjTOmtQjwXv8Cq78QdpVUkMk_CeRpuezypbrRSqwFccvgxidL9kqnU4uev1gxLfkf9tsG4_vFhEnZSvNJnZV7vac6yXqt4wGYNaVLJhJ19XiGk86gAeWeU7HkgKeFbl834t9qa9ZyeDKXNvfBXRyEX0ZH4Y3Y7K1flWXva42PNvq06kblfimgpFW5Jw7I-dj3CIwU1ct9H8ykm9zfn19212bKG7qcy0tnD9B-FqoP0kCOKwwKubV8TZyiqnTwXezqS-mJWV5KTjlqRnvqp3Ot67lXkUtEtvNFrJj8HtCQt_0AVgkCQfuLMWhqejX3Aa0AkzPfj-QsnBTsHq_5R17gwbg1wzJw/M7BOW1TGAfyMv4klkBfXTwOdVePI8D9P/18" target="_blank"&gt;创下新低&lt;/a&gt;，民主党人在贸易战方面似乎嗅到了弱点。该党的一些大人物正在抓住特朗普的失败之机，发起一场民粹主义选举年运动，将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/hFFdUB4GLghYUHtYxKTuX5lPU5l3lxbVdv5T0idPnXS6t1dUZsPlcwBXTO2TBO1q1w1_V4NnBbZUxyrILyeOJMhPjTawD6OBrG3yaKLEdrq5zOc_IDteOhb7lLBX0Pdq4U0kP1fpkgUBjcVFMxgEfTx8VT1LWojf_zaJCBNptiGwlrfd13tdH7EKTG-OCq6YH9sYgtoP-FtCpzMoOjXbuud6RL4ghPMjCHOfqUVMWXLiSoByDsYuGQfsZNWOJ8J1RlkGVFpI8FuJdL3DvkrKBvyMhdOksGu4ZkHNeK6gtuFBaSbij2YrDV8pBHvuBVEQwLPcK-Lr_ixl8f4F1Fd98ciJNUQkgf09iIgrDVNcMh0ShAbk155JtxNbaQ/v46lBlpvwprS-XcD95cq3K3927tk9NyH/18" target="_blank"&gt;所有数十亿美元的关税退还给纳税人&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;— &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TQbIUklvMctQ38ozlURmaiW0e4Xk8EgryzSOxbC7hgGyr_B6rkrtzbBuOrxi6teqCXXxKb8Xs7XOH9hTQQ3g8PZ5FMG5E1nJNwxRJnNgFm064TjfWrqJqA5Wmyk1l4pKKRxau9D6U6B5sxnYeuFdGW8Q3vQMbPY1SpLlugf82Y7SJIA832nJ457QgCNCQz5zSsluaASc6XR4Md9NYzUG9Ric55b9oNtBTHrsmz-aTyG_WSZCV6IdPbkqV-_gAYI7IG3vwL3URX4qf3WFnNtMlJOl8eQJwXTPVGy_IJ4EhnbqBehgITxD0-bRvcazJu9y8xeixr2UI_Q3VBNY7MvtWlp4zC_pDmGpWkBu5mO-J697b4YM0Ks44r2T0IA/1HxVRiAKxGh26rU0ecVVIITGTJT3aiju/18" target="_blank"&gt;大卫·E·罗维拉&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&